A violent altercation erupted in Port Elizabeth s busy Rink Street yesterday as an alleged bank card scam captured on video left a student bitten and bruised after a scuffle with three other ATM users. While police are still investigating the incident, the dramatic footage shows two women accompanied by a man beating and tugging on Chris Harding, 30, accusing him of stealing money withdrawn by one of the women at an ATM.For more on the story visit HeraldLIVE:WATCH: Attack at ATM leaves man bitten and bruised